&lt;/span>
&lt;/h4>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>we use the term &lt;strong>plastic&lt;/strong> to describe permanent deformation&lt;/li>
&lt;li>之所以是Plastic，是因为它derives from the Greek &lt;strong>plastikos&lt;/strong> meaning to sculpt&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h5 class="relative group">Changes After Plastic Deformation
&lt;div id="changes-after-plastic-deformation" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
